'''Stamina wood''' is an [[engineered wood]] product made of [[wood veneer|veneers]] that have been dyed, then impregnated with phenolic [[resin]] and compressed under high pressure and heat. The result is a material that can be worked with woodworking tools, then sanded and buffed to a high luster.
