'''Branding''' is an easy and economical way to permanently mark anything that burns ([[wood]], [[leather]], [[plastic]], [[rubber]], [[Cork (material)|cork]], food, [[soap]], [[wax]], etc.). This is done by either a fire-heated tool or an electrically-heated tool, which is pressed onto the object, leaving behind a mark with the shape of the impressed tool.

